4573.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4573.description: Nella and Trinket accidently agree to attend both Garrett and Minatori's sleepovers on the same night. // Garrett and Blaine disobey the rules and sneak out at night to see a fantastical star.

4574.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4574.description: Blaine's fancy cousin Olivia visits and questions Nella's ability to be both a princess and a knight. // When Nella loses a knightly contest, she's determined to improve by practicing.

10998.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10998.description: Nella searches for a magical crystal to make it snow for their annual 'Snow Festival'. // Nella and her friends must play as a team to win the Castlehaven gobletball tournament.

10999.title: Nella The Princess Knight
10999.description: While camping with the Knight Trekkers, Blaine goes to extreme lengths to earn his first badge. // Nella finally brings two arguing groups of dragons together, but Trinket accidentally reignites their rivalry.

17076.title: Nella The Princess Knight
17076.description: Nella bravely journeys to track down a wicked wizard, who has taken all of the kingdom's fancy things. But she has to rely on her own inner courage after he takes her knightly heart pendant too!

17077.title: Nella The Princess Knight
17077.description: Trinket is hesitant to enter the Castlehaven Rollerfest until she discovers a pair of 'magical' roller skates. // Blaine gets jealous when Garrett is cast as the part he wants in the big school play.

22870.title: Nella The Princess Knight
22870.description: Flutter gets jealous when Nella asks Flapper to deliver her mail. // Nella must teach three hydra sisters how to take turns before they ruin this year's Harvest Festival.

22871.title: Nella The Princess Knight
22871.description: A selfish giant takes all of the kingdom's water for himself. // When Nella and the gang run out of lemons for their lemonade stand, they embark on a journey of epic proportions to find more.

29177.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29177.description: Nella and her friends get lost in Minatori's maze. // Miscommunication between Nella and Garrett causes their invention at the Royal Science Expo to go wrong.

29178.title: Nella The Princess Knight
29178.description: After Trinket's horn is bent in an accident, Nella helps her find a wise unicorn to fix it. // Nella and Trinket go on a quest to retrieve Trinket's childhood toy when she accidentally gives it away.

35848.title: Nella The Princess Knight
35848.description: When the wicked wizard steals Garrett's knightly trading cards before the big trading convention, Nella is determined to get them back. // Nella and Trinket compete to make the best ice-cream.

35849.title: Nella The Princess Knight
35849.description: Nella and the gang must avoid getting their clothes dirty before a fancy party but it proves harder than it sounds. // Nella accompanies Snowpuff the dragon on a quest to find a legendary wishing well.

42243.title: Nella The Princess Knight
42243.description: Nella and her friends are invited to a party in the mysterious kingdom of Sparkleburg but no one knows where it is! // When Blaine finds himself in peril on a class climbing trip, it's up to Nella to help him!

42244.title: Nella The Princess Knight
42244.description: When bad weather ruins their plans, Nella and her friends go on a quest inside the castle. // During a cute critter watching trip, Olivia causes big problems by feeding a Chompling lunch.

49148.title: Nella The Princess Knight
49148.description: When Badalf the wicked wizard takes Nella and Olivia's musical instruments they have to work together to get them back! // Clod moves in with Trinket whilst his stable undergoes roof repairs.

49149.title: Nella The Princess Knight
49149.description: When Trinket is mysteriously 'frozen' at the Castlehaven Carnival everyone blames Badalf. // Nella embarks on an adventure to find rare ingredients for Trinket's special nail polish.

55674.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55674.description: Nella goes on a quest for Bling Berries in the Murkberry Mines so she can make her mom's favorite pancakes for breakfast! // Nella and Blaine must find three baby dragons when they go missing from a play-date.

55675.title: Nella The Princess Knight
55675.description: When Nella's sword gets an amazing upgrade she finds it difficult to master its new power. // It's the Castlehaven Jousting Tournament and all the gang want to win!

62229.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62229.description: Nella and her friends take part in an action packed Go-kart race! // Nella and Blaine search for the mysterious Moat Lake Monster.

62230.title: Nella The Princess Knight
62230.description: After a display of true courage, Trinket receives a sparkling new carriage from the Unicorn of the Lake. // Nella and Cici combine their talents to form The Castlehaven Rescue Club.

68203.title: Nella The Princess Knight
68203.description: Nella and her friends discover a kingdom in the clouds. // When Trinket and Olivia are turned into icky lizards, Nella and the gang must find the antidote.

68204.title: Nella The Princess Knight
68204.description: Nella, Garrett and Blaine compete for an annual bravery award with chaotic consequences. // Badalf the Wicked Wizard steals a magical saber that can turn things into sand.

74598.title: Nella The Princess Knight
74598.description: Long before she was Nella the Princess Knight, Nella of Castlehaven was a young princess dreaming of adventure. But when she meets a lost unicorn, Nella finds the courage to make her dreams come true by becoming a Princess Knight.

74599.title: Nella The Princess Knight
74599.description: Nella and her grandparents work together to stop a dragon flower that's frightening her kingdom. // When Munchie the dragon eats Nella and Garrett's homework, the friends must get it back before school starts.

81244.title: Nella The Princess Knight
81244.description: When the Wicked Wizard's pet goat Terry becomes a goatzilla on Norma's first birthday, Nella and the gang must save the day. // When Nella and Trinket are invited to a Minotaur tea-party, Trinket has a tough time taking part in the festivities.

81245.title: Nella The Princess Knight
81245.description: When Bogner the Bog-Troll takes Nella's bounce-house as her new home, she accidently takes Clod too; who is still bouncing inside! // Castlehaven begins to sink when the Diggykin's build their underground kingdom beneath Nella's.

88087.title: Nella The Princess Knight
88087.description: Blaine gets less than he bargained for when he scouts for his very own steed with Nella. // When Trinket loses her voice before a special duet, she and Nella must journey to the Shimmering Steamspring for a cure.

88088.title: Nella The Princess Knight
88088.description: It's the showdown of the century as Nella and her Dad square off with a fearsome gladiator! // Nella and the gang journey to a carriage showcase, but Clod worries that Garret's new go-kart will steal his thunder.

94697.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94697.description: Nella is sent on a hair-raising rescue when Trinket is pressured into copying her friends. // Blaine serves Nella a culinary catastrophe when tries to hide his passion for cooking.

94698.title: Nella The Princess Knight
94698.description: When Olivia's sparkly ball is lost behind the bowling lanes, Nella ventures into a bowling wonderland to get it back. // When a trickster villain slips away with a treasured wedding ring, Nella must get it back before the ceremony begins.
